1
00:00:05,340 --> 00:00:10,100
Rumor has it there were four mysterious sects in the Jianghu.

2
00:00:10,820 --> 00:00:14,460
According to motivation, skills and sects, they are divided into

3
00:00:14,580 --> 00:00:18,380
Mojin, Faqiu, Banshan and Xieling.

4
00:00:20,820 --> 00:00:24,100
Faqiu and Mojin are jointly called Mojin Captain.

5
00:00:24,380 --> 00:00:28,980
They are good at seeking treasures and the Book of Changes,

6
00:00:29,300 --> 00:00:33,180
while the Banshan and Xieling sects are rarely recorded

7
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:35,260
who are more mysterious.

8
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:39,620
It is said that the Xieling sect depends on strength.

9
00:00:40,540 --> 00:00:42,740
Thousands of its disciples work together

10
00:00:42,980 --> 00:00:46,660
and they can move a mountain to explore treasures.

11
00:00:46,780 --> 00:00:49,220
So it is called Xieling.

12
00:00:50,140 --> 00:00:51,900
The Banshan sect depends on skills.

13
00:00:52,140 --> 00:00:53,340
They are not seeking for treasures

14
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:56,500
but for elixir.

15
00:00:56,940 --> 00:01:00,580
For thousands of years
Banshan has been seeking for the Dust Bead

16
00:01:00,980 --> 00:01:03,620
to lift the curse of their clansmen.

17
00:01:04,380 --> 00:01:07,140
Originally, Xieling and Banshan each goes their own way.

18
00:01:07,220 --> 00:01:09,340
However, the fate brings them together

19
00:01:09,420 --> 00:01:14,620
risking lives in the mysterious and dangerous Bottle Mountain

20
00:01:15,140 --> 00:01:19,780
to perform an earth-shattering act.

21
00:01:31,980 --> 00:01:39,900
=Candle in the Tomb: the Wrath of Time=

22
00:01:40,220 --> 00:01:43,460
=Episode 17=

23
00:01:58,860 --> 00:01:59,780
Leader.

24
00:02:00,780 --> 00:02:02,260
Don't blame yourself so hard.

25
00:02:02,700 --> 00:02:04,100
This is our fate.

26
00:02:04,780 --> 00:02:05,980
You were poisoned

27
00:02:06,540 --> 00:02:07,700
and you couldn't control yourself.

28
00:02:10,060 --> 00:02:12,460
If the leader of Banshan sect
is a reasonable person,

29
00:02:13,700 --> 00:02:15,620
he wouldn't blame this on you.

30
00:02:18,220 --> 00:02:19,740
The people of Xiangxi

31
00:02:20,180 --> 00:02:21,420
are still suffering.

32
00:02:21,740 --> 00:02:23,020
They are in urgent need of our help.

33
00:02:23,820 --> 00:02:25,900
Leader, it's not the right time
for being emotional.

34
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:26,820
Boss.

35
00:02:27,300 --> 00:02:28,740
Partridge Whistle goes up the mountain alone.

36
00:02:29,260 --> 00:02:30,580
He said the tomb of Yuan Dynasty
is on the top of mountain.

37
00:02:49,900 --> 00:02:51,820
The body of the Bottle Mountain
looks like a calabash.

38
00:02:52,860 --> 00:02:54,700
The mountainside is as hollow as
a bottle's stomach.

39
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:57,100
The Elixir Palace was built inside.

40
00:02:57,820 --> 00:02:59,140
People who tried to find the tomb

41
00:02:59,700 --> 00:03:01,780
all focused on the grottoes,

42
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:04,500
but ignored the opening of the bottle
which is at the top of the mountain.

43
00:03:04,820 --> 00:03:07,580
Mausoleums were always built underground
since ancient times.

44
00:03:08,380 --> 00:03:10,160
Even if they had to plough the mountain
into the shape of a coffin

45
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:11,860
or break stones,

46
00:03:12,660 --> 00:03:15,900
they'd hide the mausoleum
into the deepest part of the mountainside.

47
00:03:16,900 --> 00:03:18,300
We really can't explore
the tomb of the Bottle Mountain

48
00:03:18,860 --> 00:03:20,780
in a normal way.

49
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:23,780
They should put the mausoleum
on the top of the mountain

50
00:03:24,460 --> 00:03:26,300
and place a fake tomb at the foot

51
00:03:26,820 --> 00:03:28,340
to distract people.

52
00:03:32,940 --> 00:03:34,900
It looks like that the reason why
people from Yuan Dynasty

53
00:03:35,980 --> 00:03:37,540
changed the Elixir Palace into a tomb

54
00:03:38,340 --> 00:03:40,780
was to suppress the cave here.

55
00:03:42,060 --> 00:03:43,580
This is called the Suppressing Sorcery.

56
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:47,060
Using mausoleums to suppress the evil things

57
00:03:47,420 --> 00:03:48,780
is really rare.

58
00:03:49,820 --> 00:03:50,900
Besides,

59
00:03:51,180 --> 00:03:53,220
the Suppressing Sorcery
of the Hmong Village nearby

60
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:55,860
is also carried out at the topmost of their house.

61
00:03:56,820 --> 00:03:57,940
In this way,

62
00:03:59,380 --> 00:04:02,180
the tomb must be on the mountaintop.

63
00:04:06,432 --> 00:04:07,056
Alright.

64
00:04:10,208 --> 00:04:11,820
Now that we know the specific location of the tomb,

65
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:12,860
