150
00:11:37,460 --> 00:11:38,380
What did you hide?

151
00:11:38,460 --> 00:11:39,740
Sir, he is slinging mud at me!

152
00:11:39,940 --> 00:11:41,180
Last time,
it was also him who asked for trouble.

153
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:42,420
Me? Asking for trouble?

154
00:11:42,420 --> 00:11:44,300
Do you have guts
to show us what you stole?

155
00:12:15,420 --> 00:12:16,940
Wait! Watch out for the machinery.

156
00:12:20,460 --> 00:12:21,260
Brother.

157
00:12:21,940 --> 00:12:23,380
No! Brother Partridge Whistle, stop!

158
00:12:24,100 --> 00:12:25,100
Mind your own business.

159
00:12:47,580 --> 00:12:49,340
