Why is the mountain shaking?

160
00:12:49,620 --> 00:12:50,780
Is it an earthquake?

161
00:12:59,500 --> 00:13:00,260
Boss.

162
00:13:07,940 --> 00:13:08,700
What's going on?

163
00:13:15,820 --> 00:13:16,460
Brother.

164
00:13:16,460 --> 00:13:17,500
You were so scared before.

165
00:13:17,580 --> 00:13:18,460
Did you wet yourself?

166
00:13:18,460 --> 00:13:19,140
Shut up.

167
00:13:19,140 --> 00:13:20,540
