you would wet yourself too.

168
00:13:20,660 --> 00:13:21,580
If I fell down from here,

169
00:13:21,620 --> 00:13:22,780
I would crash into pieces.

170
00:13:38,256 --> 00:13:40,380
Partridge Whistle, it's too dangerous here.
Don't go in there.

171
00:13:40,380 --> 00:13:40,860
Let's go.

172
00:13:41,700 --> 00:13:42,180
Let's get out of here.

173
00:13:42,820 --> 00:13:43,580
Brother.

174
00:13:44,260 --> 00:13:45,900
It's too dangerous.
Let's go out.

175
00:13:46,300 --> 00:13:47,220
Partridge Whistle.

176
00:13:47,380 --> 00:13:48,020
Let's get out of here.

177
00:13:48,020 --> 00:13:48,380
Go!

178
00:13:48,380 --> 00:13:49,100
Hurry up!

179
00:13:52,340 --> 00:13:53,340
Run!

180
00:13:53,540 --> 00:13:54,420
- Run!
- Run!

181
00:14:01,820 --> 00:14:02,740
Get out of here!

182
00:14:15,260 --> 00:14:15,860
Hold on.

183
00:14:15,980 --> 00:14:16,820
Cripple Huama.

184
00:14:16,820 --> 00:14:18,620
Ask our men to jump across the mountain!

185
00:14:18,620 --> 00:14:19,100
Hurry up!

186
00:14:19,100 --> 00:14:20,740
Now! Or you will die!
The mountain is falling down.

187
00:14:20,740 --> 00:14:21,540
Stop looking back.

188
00:14:21,780 --> 00:14:23,060
We can search for the Dust Bead anytime.

189
00:14:23,060 --> 00:14:23,980
You wanna die here?

190
00:15:03,340 --> 00:15:04,100
Let's go!

191
00:15:04,380 --> 00:15:05,780
If you won't leave,
then I'll stay here with you.

192
00:15:24,752 --> 00:15:25,380
Leader!

193
00:15:25,780 --> 00:15:27,540
Leader! Don't… Leader!

194
00:15:27,740 --> 00:15:29,140
Leader!

195
00:15:29,380 --> 00:15:30,020
Leader!

196
00:15:30,460 --> 00:15:31,780
Leader!

197
00:16:16,580 --> 00:16:17,620
Let go of me.

198
00:16:19,380 --> 00:16:20,300
Let go of me!

199
00:16:20,820 --> 00:16:22,180
One is better than none.

200
00:16:23,780 --> 00:16:25,740
You are the only one left of Banshan sect.

201
00:16:26,860 --> 00:16:27,740
You have to live…

202
00:16:29,260 --> 00:16:30,700
No, I can't let you die!

203
00:17:03,780 --> 00:17:04,660
How are you feeling?

204
00:17:04,820 --> 00:17:05,740
Can you move?

205
00:17:08,060 --> 00:17:09,620
If not, climb on my back.

206
00:17:36,860 --> 00:17:38,540
Don't run. Come back.

207
00:17:38,660 --> 00:17:39,660
Pick them up.

208
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:40,820
Pick them up.

209
00:17:43,220 --> 00:17:44,220
Come back.

210
00:17:45,700 --> 00:17:46,740
Pick them up.

211
00:17:55,340 --> 00:17:56,180
Let's go.

212
00:17:56,620 --> 00:17:58,540
Hurry! Or we will all die here!

213
00:18:01,420 --> 00:18:02,060
Hurry up!

214
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:03,140
Get out of my way!

215
00:18:03,260 --> 00:18:04,700
Let me leave first. Come on!

216
00:18:10,700 --> 00:18:11,860
Come on! All of you!

217
00:18:15,180 --> 00:18:16,180
Which way?

218
00:18:16,180 --> 00:18:17,180
Here! This way!

219
00:18:36,980 --> 00:18:37,700
Run!

220
00:18:37,740 --> 00:18:38,220
Run!

221
00:18:42,180 --> 00:18:42,900
Run!

222
00:19:13,820 --> 00:19:14,860
Leader!

223
00:19:16,140 --> 00:19:17,500
My dearest Leader.

224
00:19:18,420 --> 00:19:19,820
You are still alive.

225
00:19:20,420 --> 00:19:21,260
Great.

226
00:19:21,820 --> 00:19:22,660
That's great!

227
00:19:23,980 --> 00:19:24,940
The mountain fell down.

228
00:19:25,340 --> 00:19:27,500
Some of my men died, and some escaped.

229
00:19:27,740 --> 00:19:28,700
Most of the treasures

230
00:19:28,900 --> 00:19:30,540
were buried in the cave.

231
00:19:31,020 --> 00:19:33,260
We suffered a double loss this time.

232
00:19:34,300 --> 00:19:35,140
What should we do?

233
00:19:37,500 --> 00:19:38,700
It's all my fault.

234
00:19:38,820 --> 00:19:39,660
What?

235
00:19:41,020 --> 00:19:42,180
I shouldn't have come.

236
00:19:44,260 --> 00:19:45,300
It's all my fault.

237
00:19:47,300 --> 00:19:48,380
My fault.

238
00:19:51,700 --> 00:19:53,180
So you don't know what to do either.

239
00:19:53,180 --> 00:19:53,940
Commander Luo.

240
00:19:54,900 --> 00:19:56,340
We'd better go back to the Mortuary first

241
00:19:57,420 --> 00:19:58,500
and then discuss what to do the next.

242
00:20:03,100 --> 00:20:07,260
Chen Yulou watched huge rocks falling down,
killing so many people.

243
00:20:07,540 --> 00:20:09,540
