and suddenly is filled with anger.

245
00:20:13,060 --> 00:20:15,940
It seems like that all his desire to succeed

246
00:20:15,940 --> 00:20:18,060
has fallen down together with the Bottle Mountain.

247
00:20:18,740 --> 00:20:24,140
