251
00:20:31,940 --> 00:20:34,180
directly staggering away.

252
00:21:20,900 --> 00:21:21,820
I'm sorry.

253
00:21:22,180 --> 00:21:23,740
I shouldn't have been so mean to you.

254
00:21:26,580 --> 00:21:27,420
It's not your fault.

255
00:21:28,900 --> 00:21:30,060
What happened just now

256
00:21:31,380 --> 00:21:33,620
reminds me of the past.

257
00:21:46,820 --> 00:21:47,980
My father told me something

258
00:21:48,820 --> 00:21:49,980
before he died.

259
00:21:51,580 --> 00:21:53,180
He asked me to live a good life.

260
00:21:55,020 --> 00:21:55,900
At that time,

261
00:21:56,860 --> 00:21:58,460
I watched my father

262
00:21:59,620 --> 00:22:01,620
get killed by those bullies.

263
00:22:02,180 --> 00:22:03,540
I know about your past.

264
00:22:05,060 --> 00:22:07,220
You then set fire to burn all those bullies.

265
00:22:13,300 --> 00:22:14,260
That was not me.

266
00:22:15,860 --> 00:22:17,340
But everyone believed it was me

267
00:22:17,660 --> 00:22:18,940
who killed the bully's entire family.

268
00:22:19,660 --> 00:22:21,100
They thought I wanted to take revenge.

269
00:22:22,980 --> 00:22:23,900
Actually,

270
00:22:25,140 --> 00:22:27,740
they just caught in a fire accidentally.

271
00:22:30,940 --> 00:22:32,740
The God was punishing them.

272
00:22:34,020 --> 00:22:35,140
But I really wish

273
00:22:37,500 --> 00:22:39,820
it was me who avenged my father.

274
00:22:40,380 --> 00:22:41,860
Only I was too young at that time,

275
00:22:42,780 --> 00:22:43,740
I wasn't brave enough.

276
00:22:45,540 --> 00:22:46,900
Just let them die easily like that.

277
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:49,820
My poor father.

278
00:23:10,420 --> 00:23:11,780
No matter what happened yesterday,

279
00:23:13,500 --> 00:23:15,340
