280
00:23:16,820 --> 00:23:17,900
Just like the sun.

281
00:23:18,740 --> 00:23:20,220
The sun falls every day,

282
00:23:21,500 --> 00:23:22,460
but tomorrow,

283
00:23:23,340 --> 00:23:24,580
it will rise up again.

284
00:24:13,260 --> 00:24:13,980
Commander Luo.

285
00:24:14,660 --> 00:24:15,660
Leader Chen is…

286
00:24:21,820 --> 00:24:23,500
Man proposes, God disposes.

287
00:24:23,860 --> 00:24:25,540
Who could have foreseen
that the Bottle Mountain would collapse?

288
00:24:27,900 --> 00:24:28,980
I think that

289
00:24:29,140 --> 00:24:30,100
we can't rely on anyone else

290
00:24:30,660 --> 00:24:31,620
but ourselves.

291
00:24:33,420 --> 00:24:34,180
Yang.

292
00:24:37,980 --> 00:24:39,300
We should go there again.

293
00:24:39,380 --> 00:24:41,232
We two must carry on.

294
00:24:41,408 --> 00:24:42,300
We can't accept failure just like that.

295
00:24:43,220 --> 00:24:44,060
Commander Luo.

296
00:24:44,660 --> 00:24:45,540
Don't worry.

297
00:24:46,260 --> 00:24:47,700
I definitely won't let you down.

298
00:24:50,340 --> 00:24:51,100
Good.

299
00:24:54,860 --> 00:24:55,700
Cripple Huama.

300
00:24:56,180 --> 00:24:57,060
Red Girl.

301
00:24:57,740 --> 00:24:58,580
The leader of Banshan sect…

302
00:24:58,660 --> 00:24:59,980
You both made it!

303
00:25:05,180 --> 00:25:06,060
Where's Leader?

304
00:25:06,940 --> 00:25:08,340
He thought you were…

305
00:25:08,820 --> 00:25:09,900
He was distressed and regretful.

306
00:25:09,980 --> 00:25:11,060
And he was quite depressed.

307
00:25:11,220 --> 00:25:13,220
When he came back, seeing our men suffer heavy losses,

308
00:25:13,220 --> 00:25:14,460
he was even more defeated,

309
00:25:14,660 --> 00:25:15,580
and couldn't forgive himself.

310
00:25:16,580 --> 00:25:17,500
Let me go check on him.

311
00:25:17,980 --> 00:25:18,780
That won't work.

312
00:25:18,980 --> 00:25:20,220
I've already tried to talk him out of it.

313
00:25:20,500 --> 00:25:21,740
But he's been like this since he came back.

314
00:25:21,820 --> 00:25:22,940
He wouldn't even say a word.

315
00:25:46,980 --> 00:25:47,940
You're still alive?

316
00:25:50,580 --> 00:25:51,580
That's awesome.

317
00:25:54,820 --> 00:25:55,620
Red Girl.

318
00:25:56,860 --> 00:25:58,380
Go pack your things.

319
00:25:58,940 --> 00:26:00,380
Let's get out of here when you're done.

320
00:26:02,820 --> 00:26:04,060
And you too.

321
00:26:04,420 --> 00:26:05,300
Let's leave here.

322
00:26:06,060 --> 00:26:06,660
Leave here.

323
00:26:06,660 --> 00:26:07,860
Chen Yulou!

324
00:26:07,860 --> 00:26:09,060
You junk!

325
00:26:09,260 --> 00:26:11,140
Our Banshan sect has had failures for thousands of years

326
00:26:11,220 --> 00:26:12,500
since we started to search for the Dust Bead.

327
00:26:12,940 --> 00:26:14,940
Countless people have died
from generation to generation.

328
00:26:15,100 --> 00:26:16,420
If we were all like you,

329
00:26:16,420 --> 00:26:18,180
then our Banshan sect is long gone.

330
00:26:20,460 --> 00:26:21,580
I failed.

331
00:26:22,380 --> 00:26:23,440
Failed!

332
00:26:23,440 --> 00:26:24,260
Don't you understand?

333
00:26:24,260 --> 00:26:25,660
You have to accept it.

334
00:26:29,620 --> 00:26:30,900
I thought

335
00:26:32,940 --> 00:26:35,900
the leader of the Xieling sect was a real man.

336
00:26:37,060 --> 00:26:38,980
But it turns out you are also a coward.

337
00:26:48,940 --> 00:26:49,700
You're right.

338
00:26:50,580 --> 00:26:51,860
I'm a coward.

339
00:26:52,220 --> 00:26:54,220
I didn't think I was one.

340
00:26:55,660 --> 00:26:56,704
But now I know.

341
00:26:57,500 --> 00:26:59,820
I am a coward, so what?

342
00:27:05,220 --> 00:27:06,620
Then how about the people who died inside?

343
00:27:07,500 --> 00:27:08,580
Were they cowards?

344
00:27:09,260 --> 00:27:10,700
They died for nothing?

345
00:27:12,660 --> 00:27:14,100
Yeah, they died for nothing!

346
00:27:18,980 --> 00:27:19,900
What do you want?

347
00:27:21,420 --> 00:27:22,700
You want me to die for them?

348
00:27:23,700 --> 00:27:24,700
I don't care.

349
00:27:25,100 --> 00:27:26,980
I'm just a cheap dog.

350
00:27:33,940 --> 00:27:35,300
Indeed, your life is nothing.

351
00:27:35,500 --> 00:27:36,500
Nothing!

352
00:27:37,300 --> 00:27:38,980
But you've still got your men.

353
00:27:39,860 --> 00:27:42,700
You have to finish the missions waiting for you.

354
00:27:43,140 --> 00:27:45,220
Or the Xieling sect will become a joke in the Jianghu

355
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:46,340
and never get to rise again.

356
00:27:48,300 --> 00:27:49,420
Which one is more important?

357
00:27:51,700 --> 00:27:52,860
Think it over.

358
00:29:23,580 --> 00:29:24,420
Does it hurt?

359
00:29:28,180 --> 00:29:29,100
Hold on.

360
00:29:33,620 --> 00:29:34,940
I still owe you a question.

361
00:29:35,100 --> 00:29:35,980
What question?

362
00:29:37,380 --> 00:29:39,620
You asked Hualing how old I was
when I joined the Banshan sect.

363
00:29:43,460 --> 00:29:44,260
How old were you?

364
00:29:44,340 --> 00:29:45,180
13.

365
00:29:55,740 --> 00:29:58,140
The elder brother of Banshan
thought I was too weak.

366
00:29:59,900 --> 00:30:01,100
In order to join the Banshan sect,

367
00:30:01,500 --> 00:30:03,420
I had to prove my capabilities.

368
00:30:04,140 --> 00:30:04,900
So,

369
00:30:06,580 --> 00:30:08,300
you went to the wolf valley all alone.

370
00:30:10,140 --> 00:30:11,860
There were a dozen of wolves there.

371
00:30:13,700 --> 00:30:15,140
I used little wolves as baits

372
00:30:15,780 --> 00:30:18,020
to seduce big wolves one by one,

373
00:30:19,420 --> 00:30:20,380
and then killed them all.

374
00:30:22,860 --> 00:30:24,500
You were only 13 years old.

375
00:30:25,620 --> 00:30:27,020
Weren't you afraid that you couldn't
walk out of the wolf valley alive?

376
00:30:28,180 --> 00:30:29,140
If I couldn't,

377
00:30:30,420 --> 00:30:32,460
it meant that I was not capable enough.

378
00:30:34,740 --> 00:30:36,220
I wouldn't be able to save my mother

379
00:30:37,060 --> 00:30:38,300
and I couldn't join the Bansan sect.

380
00:30:38,580 --> 00:30:40,460
Then I deserved to die there.

381
00:30:47,860 --> 00:30:49,060
Parents in the world

382
00:30:50,340 --> 00:30:51,860
all hope their children

383
00:30:51,860 --> 00:30:53,020
can live a good life.

384
00:31:10,700 --> 00:31:12,220
We Zhagelama people

385
00:31:12,660 --> 00:31:15,300
were cursed by the Guidong people 2000 years ago.

386
00:31:16,740 --> 00:31:19,140
It is said that only the Dust Bead
can break the curse.

387
00:31:22,700 --> 00:31:24,180
My father was in the Banshan sect too.

388
00:31:26,380 --> 00:31:28,220
He died in the tomb and never came back.

389
00:31:30,220 --> 00:31:31,184
And my mother,

390
00:31:33,888 --> 00:31:34,976
she died because of the curse.
